{"tid":1696092,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"修例風波：國泰港龍空姐涉非法集結    遭調離職務","createTime":"2019-11-06T03:36:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-07T17:06:22.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"93133b3f2f6743cc217c9a1f29b719e1b0f51153","tid":1696092,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T03:36:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/修例風波國泰港龍空姐涉非法集結-遭調離職務-003333514.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E9%A2%A8%E6%B3%A2%E5%9C%8B%E6%B3%B0%E6%B8%AF%E9%BE%8D%E7%A9%BA%E5%A7%90%E6%B6%89%E9%9D%9E%E6%B3%95%E9%9B%86%E7%B5%90-%E9%81%AD%E8%AA%BF%E9%9B%A2%E8%81%B7%E5%8B%99-003333514.html&d=5WD1fpiCBK613UyTU9OnX3r2%2BPVmRcyv9paqmPGdWjc%3D&h=8dc4eb77\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/修例風波國泰港龍空姐涉非法集結-遭調離職務-003333514.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://site-120792.mozfiles.com/files/120792/Cathay-Pacific-Flight-Attendant-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsite-120792.mozfiles.com%2Ffiles%2F120792%2FCathay-Pacific-Flight-Attendant-1.jpg&h=8146967e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n東網得悉，有國泰空姐參與反修例示威被捕，她涉嫌在11月2日於銅鑼灣非法集結及未能出示身份證。<br />\n<br />\n國泰港龍航空表示，該名員工已被調離所有職務，國泰不會就個別個案的處理詳情作出回應。國泰視維護航空安全為首要任務，定必嚴肅處理及跟進有關事件。國泰對任何不合法活動持零容忍態度，任何違規行為將會受到紀律處分。"},{"pid":"6d7d51c8c6482a07a38438ab9e9c1a72f9cf9ccb","tid":1696092,"uid":194745,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T13:21:08.000Z","msg":"去台灣，長榮/中華<br />\n<br />\n去日本， JAL ANA PEACH<br />\n<br />\n去韓國， 大韓 韓亞<br />\n<br />\n去泰國， Air Thai Emirates Thai Smile<br />\n<br />\n去歐洲 英航，三寶, virgin Air France lufthansa<br />\n<br />\n去澳洲  qantas scoot Air NZ<br />\n<br />\n去美國 AA United<br />\n<br />\n去中國  冇計 國泰港龍"},{"pid":"fabce2bc2980a499a0058be6cb55d66ee67f0ee8","tid":1696092,"uid":312526,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T13:24:43.000Z","msg":"我想搞boycott太古 <br />\n幫我地靚女空姐"},{"pid":"570bfef0573d4e8cf8